  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Mesenchymal Stem Cell in Treating Kidney Fibrosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1 Clinical Trial Using Mesenchymal Stem Cell as Individualized Medicine to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy in Kidney Fibrosis</official_title>
