  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Written informed consent.

          2. Glomerular sclerosis ratio ≤ 50%.

          3. Renal tubulointerstitial fibrosis ratio ≤ 50%.

          4. Negative pregnancy test.

          5. Moderately active disease under standard treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1. Severe infection and cardiovascular disease, shock, secondary liver disease and
        malignant tumor.
      </textblock>
